category: Devel
requires: mingw64-x86_64-curl mingw64-x86_64-gcc-core mingw64-x86_64-zlib mingw64-x86_64-zstd
sdesc: "MySQL client library for Win64 toolchain"
ldesc: "MariaDB Connector/C is used to connect applications developed in
C or C++ to MariaDB and MySQL databases. MariaDB Connector/C has exactly the
same API as the MySQL Connector/C for MySQL 5.5."

